<br>
Example.. with one group and time to camp.. you could get a Noc Blade in a day, you could get a Sword of Pain in a day.. your approaching the level to get this stuff yourself.. save your cash for stuff like an AC20 cloak or the best haste you can get...<br>
<br>
nothing sux more that geting outfitted then advancing 3 levels and finding out you need to completly upgrade again.<br>
<br>
Quest armor all the way.. put your resouces into getting the chance to get some.<br>
<br>
Laterz<br>
